          "name": "Pathfinder #209: Destroyer's Doom",
          "page": 86,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "The fierce bull of Zagresh is an enormous, easily riled bovine with sharp horns like a stag's. The bulls are bred and raised for sport as well as war.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
